Package: dataAnim
Title: Visualise data transformation with animations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Charco", "Hui", email = "phui285@aucklanduni.ac.nz", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Many data wrangling operations can seem quite abstract,
    making them harder to understand for people new to data science.
    This package makes the ideas more concrete, and hence easier to learn, 
    by animating transformation of data tables.
Imports: 
    htmlwidgets,
    dplyr,
    jsonlite,
    tidyr,
    magrittr,
    rlang (>= 0.1.2),
    tibble
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
